Name: CreateMainTask
Id: 1
Description: Add a main task
Actors: 
Main: Project manager
Secondary: None
Pre-conditions: The main task has a subtask associated
Main flow: 
1.	The use case begins when the project manager highlights a group of tasks and selects “Create main task”
2.	The system displays the main task with a set of associated subtasks
2.1.	The information displayed by the main task is the total duration, the start day and the finish day
Alternative flows: 

Post-conditions: A new main task has been created and displays its total duration, start date, finish date and associated subtasks. 
